These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, juice
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, argentine, italian
1. the argentine is in the middle##1
2. the person drinking juice is the italian##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |    3    |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | coffee | juice   |
| Nationality      | egyptian    | argentine  | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-2::.
City: berlin, new-york, venice
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, canadian, nigerian
1. the argentine is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
2. the canadian is on the far left##1
3. the canadian is the person traveling to new-york##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3     |
| City      | new-york | berlin     | venice      |
| Nationality   | canadian | argentine | nigerian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: motorbike, quad-bike, trike
There 3 different types of food: plum, radish, raspberry
1. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person eating radish##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2    |     3     |
| Transport   | motorbike | trike  | quad-bike       |
| Food       | plum     | radish | raspberry |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: polish, chinese, mexican
The people have 3 different hobbies: card-games, puzzles, woodworking
1. the chinese is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
2. the polish is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |      3      |
| Nationality    | mexican    | chinese     | polish |
| Hobby   | woodworking | card-games | puzzles     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-5::.
3 different pets are kept: bird, guinea-pig, hedgehog
There 3 different types of food: carrot, kale, papaya
1. the person eating kale is the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person eating kale is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
4. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3     |
| Pet         | guinea-pig | bird     | hedgehog |
| Food   | papaya        | carrot | kale    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-6::.
There 3 different types of food: kiwi, plum, strawberry
3 different pets are kept: turtle, chinchilla, guinea-pig
1. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
2. the person eating plum is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
3. the person eating strawberry is the owner of the turtle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2     |   3   |
| Food        | strawberry | kiwi      | plum  |
| Pet   | turtle       | chinchilla | guinea-pig |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-7::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, roller, subway
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, ferret, goldfish
1. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the roller is the owner of the ferret##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |   3    |
| Transport   | subway      | van     | roller    |
| Pet           | chinchilla | goldfish | ferret |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-8::.
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, peach, pomegranate
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, blues, country
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
2. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the fan of country##1
3. the person eating peach is the fan of blues##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food    | pomegranate | asparagus | peach      |
| Music-Genre   | disco     | country | blues |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  librarian, security-guard, teacher
3 different pets are kept: horse, rabbit, rat
1. the owner of the horse is the security-guard##1
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
3. the security-guard is on the right of the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| Job   | teacher | security-guard | librarian  |
| Pet     | rat     | horse      | rabbit |

