.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-10::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, balloon-flower, begonia
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, zombie
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Flower      | iris   | balloon-flower    | begonia    |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | adventure | zombie |

