.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-14::.
3 different games are played: bridge, scrabble, domino
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, hedgehog
1. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person playing domino##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |    1     |       2        |      3      |
| Game   | bridge    | domino | scrabble |
| Pet   | hedgehog | chinchilla     | fish        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-15::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, ritmeester, blend
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, funk, pop
1. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far right##1
2. the fan of pop is on the left of the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the right of the fan of funk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |     3     |
| Cigar      | montecristo  | blend | ritmeester  |
| Music-Genre   | funk | pop   | classical |

