.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-16::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk, tea
There 3 different types of food: cucumber, potato, lemon
1. the person eating potato is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta | tea    |
| Food        | cucumber    | lemon | potato |

