.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-18::.
There 3 different types of food: garlic, nectarine, papaya
City: liverpool, rome, hamburg
1. the person traveling to hamburg is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person eating garlic is the person traveling to hamburg##1
3. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |
| Food    | nectarine | papaya   | garlic        |
| City   | rome    | liverpool | hamburg |

