.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-19::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, singing, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: tram, helicopter, scooter
1. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
2. the person who's hobby is singing is the person driving the scooter##1
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby         | camping | singing | sudoku |
| Transport   | tram | scooter     | helicopter  |

