.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-1-20::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: july, december, april
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: cycling, snowboarding, soccer
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2       |    3    |
| Birthday    | april | july       | december  |
| Sport   | soccer  | snowboarding | cycling |

 